# React + Tailwind Patterns

## Components

- Functional components only
- PascalCase files in `components/` (e.g. `HeroSection.tsx`)
- Section components: `components/sections/`
- Hooks co-located in `components/` (e.g. `useIsAdmin.ts`)

## Server vs client

```tsx
// Default — no directive
export default async function Page() { ... }

// Only when needed — interactivity, hooks, browser APIs
"use client";
export function MobileMenu() { ... }
```

## Figma → Tailwind

- Match spacing/sizing from Figma inspect
- Use flex/grid; avoid absolute positioning unless design requires
- `next/image` for photos; explicit width/height or `fill` + `sizes`
- Extract repeated colors/spacing to `app/globals.css` `@theme`

## Editable blocks

Wrap CMS slots:

```tsx
<EditableText
  relUrl="/about"
  blockKey="hero-title"
  placeholderContent="Title"
  placeholderTag="h1"
  className="text-4xl font-bold"
/>
```

## Styling

- Tailwind utilities primary; CSS modules optional for complex one-offs
- No inline styles except dynamic values
